OL,6,FThe will be enforced on 20mph roads
OL,7,Facross Wales.
OL,9,FGoSafe, which operates speed cameras
OL,10,Facross the country, has confirmed it
OL,11,Fwill increase monitoring from Monday,
OL,12,Fwith 15 additional cameras.
OL,14,FStronger enforcement will come in on
OL,15,Fany roads where there is evidence of
OL,16,Fsafety risks.
