OL,3,C20mph default speed limit set to be
OL,4,Cenforced on more Welsh roads
OL,6,FSpeeding drivers will be stopped when
OL,7,Fthey are caught going 26mph or above,
OL,8,Fwhich is higher than the usual
OL,9,Fenforcement threshold. The increase by
OL,10,FChief Police Officers is in place
OL,11,Fwhile the public get used to a lower
OL,12,Fspeed limit on many roads.
OL,14,FDrivers will be spoken to and given
OL,15,Fthe option of watching a presentation,
OL,16,Frather than being fined or prosecuted
OL,17,Fwhich is part of GoSafe's Operation
OL,18,FUgain which prioritises engagement
OL,19,Fover enforcement.
