OL,3,C20mph default speed limit set to be
OL,4,Cenforced on more Welsh roads
OL,6,FOf the nearly 25,000 drivers monitored
OL,7,Fby GoSafe in recent months, 97% were
OL,8,Fnot driving above 25mph, according to
OL,9,Fstatistics released by the
OL,10,Forganisation.
OL,12,FAssistant Chief Constable Trudi
OL,13,FMeyrick, roads policing lead for Wales
OL,14,Fsaid: "Introducing enforcement in new
OL,15,F20mph areas is the next step of our
OL,16,Fengagement-led approach. We have
OL,17,Fcontinued to review driver behaviour
OL,18,Fand the response to the change in
OL,19,Fdefault speed limit, whilst engaging
OL,20,Fwith communities across Wales with
OL,21,FOperation Ugain.
